org.infinispan.commons.equivalence

Class IdentityEquivalence<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.infinispan.commons.equivalence.IdentityEquivalence<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Equivalence<T>

    public class IdentityEquivalence<T>
extends Object
implements Equivalence<T>
    Equivalence implementation that uses the System.identityHashCode(Object) as hash code function.
